      "blocks": {
        "story-heading": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Local IT, Done Right",
            "size": "3xl"
          }
        },
        "story-text": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Uplink started in 2016 as a one-person operation — a laptop bag, a phone, and a list of small businesses that needed help. Eight years later, we are a team of six technicians serving the Portland metro area.</p><p>Every technician on our team is CompTIA A+ and Network+ certified. Most hold Microsoft 365 certifications. All are background-checked and insured. We show up on time, explain the problem in plain language, and fix it. That is the entire business model.</p>",
            "size": "base"
          }
        },
        "story-features": {
          "type": "features",
          "settings": {
            "features": "+ CompTIA A+ and Network+ certified\n+ Microsoft 365 certified\n+ Background-checked and insured\n+ Portland metro coverage"
          }
        }
      },
      "blocksOrder": ["story-heading", "story-text", "story-features"]
    },
